# nogc_async_immut — Immutable Persistent Data Structures for Lock-Free Concurrency
#
# This library variant provides persistent data structures with structural sharing
# and lock-free coordination primitives for concurrent programming.
#
# Architecture:
#   - PersistentMap: HAMT-based immutable hash map
#   - PersistentSet: Set wrapper over PersistentMap
#   - PersistentList: Cons list with O(1) prepend
#   - Atom: CAS-based mutable reference to immutable value
#
# Design principles:
#   - No var, no me methods (everything returns new version)
#   - Structural sharing (O(log n) updates, not O(n) copies)
#   - Lock-free coordination via CAS atoms

# Re-export submodules
# (These will be uncommented as modules are implemented)
